WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.825
Engaging deeply with our cloud partner perfectly solves the single

00:00:03.825 --> 00:00:07.650
largest structural hurdle we face in closing massive enterprise deals:

00:00:07.650 --> 00:00:11.475
a deep corporate communication gap. Our primary buyers are marketing

00:00:11.475 --> 00:00:15.300
teams who rarely understand their company's broader cloud commitments, and

00:00:15.300 --> 00:00:19.125
our sellers rarely speak directly to the IT and finance

00:00:19.125 --> 00:00:22.950
leaders who hold those macro-budgets. The cloud account manager serves

00:00:22.950 --> 00:00:26.775
as the crucial, trusted bridge actively connecting our isolated marketing

00:00:26.775 --> 00:00:30.600
champions with the ultimate financial decision-makers.
